originalText.text: Sabina is an amazing stylist! I really loved her mindful fashion approach. It was very different from my previous experiences I had with other stylists. Sabina helped me identify my personal style goals before shopping. It helped me to create a wardrobe that reflects my personality and makes me happy every day. She's a true professional!

I've always dressed in neutral, dark tones, and a friend recently suggested that I consider adding a bit more color. I had seen some of Sabina's work on Instagram and reached out - and I'm really glad that I did. Sabinaâ€™s expertise in menâ€™s style, color matching, and pattern pairing is impressive. Her approach is no-nonsense and systematic - with a direct approach about what to purchase, where, and also how to style the clothing. Everything she suggested could be mixed and matched with other pieces. As a result, I now have a catalog of outfits that I can create from the pieces she suggested. People comment positively on the color I'm infusing into my wardrobe, and it's given me confidence to continue branching out from the neutral, dark colors that have made up most of my wardrobe.

I'm taking a trip to Europe this Spring and will definitely utilize Sabina to help me prepare.
